==Emmy Awards== ''Stargate Atlantis'' was nominated for four [[Emmy Awards]]. From those, they were nominations for "Outstanding Special Visual Effects for a Series" twice, and one each for "Outsdanding Main Title Theme Music" and "Outstanding Music Composition for a Series (Dramatical Underscore)".
